哈喽大家好我是王刚
Hello everyone this is Wang Gang
本期视频为大家带来一道家常菜
In this video, I'll introduce a homestyle dish
肉末蒸蛋
Steamed egg with ground meat
首先我们在碗中打入
First, we crack three egg
鸡蛋三个
in a bowl
加入适量的盐和猪油
add Moderate amount of salt and lard
用筷子将鸡蛋搅散
mixed the eggs
再加入250毫升的温水拌匀
and add 250ml water and mix it up
然后将蛋液中的泡沫过滤
Then filter the foam in the eggs
将鸡蛋放入蒸锅中
put the bowl in steamer
碗口盖上一个碟子
cover the bowl with a plate
上汽之后盖上锅盖
cover up the steamer when steam coming up
开中小火蒸十分钟
steam the bowl in medium and small heat with 10 minutes
然后准备肉末150克
prepare 150g ground pork
加入盐，料酒和水淀粉拌匀
mix it up with salt,cooking wine and water starch
锅中加入少许食用油
add a little oil in a wok
加入肉末开小火把肉末煸香
heat medium fire of the wok and fried the ground pork
下一步开始调味
next seasoning
加入白糖提鲜
add sugar
加入生抽
add soy sauce
再加入老抽上色
add dark soy sauce
加入小葱白炒香
add chopped grenn onion and fried it
最后加入适量的
finally add moderate amount of
水淀粉勾芡
water starch 
10分钟后取出蒸蛋
remove the steamd egg after 10 minutes
将肉末铺在蒸蛋上面
cover the steamed egg with cooked ground pork
即可上菜
ready to serve
一道美味的肉末蒸蛋就制作完成
Now, a very delicious dish of steamed egg with ground meat is done!

